{"tid":210110,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD 推出新一代顯示卡產品線「Radeon RX 500」系列","createTime":"2017-04-20T16:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T06:08:08.000Z","uid":22424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfad3827eb6370bdf941c3f917682b2d6f4a13e","tid":210110,"uid":22424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T16:53:34.000Z","msg":"AMD 於日前宣布，將推出取代既有「Radeon RX 400」系列顯示卡的新一代顯示卡產品線「Radeon RX 500」系列，首波預定推出 Radeon RX 580 / 570 / 560 / 550 共 4 款產品，預估市場零售價 229 美元到 79 美元不等（折合新台幣約 6970 元到 2400 元）。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/87/0001535787.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F87%2F0001535787.JPG&h=9736b1fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n　　Radeon RX 500 系列採用改良版的 Polaris 架構繪圖處理器核心，與 Radeon RX 400 系列維持相同的 14nm FinFET 製程與晶片尺寸，透過細部的微調改良提升良率，增加有效的處理單元數量（CU）與提升運作時脈，提供較 RX 400 系列同級產品更高的處理效能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/88/0001535788.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F88%2F0001535788.JPG&h=0d89359f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25bf49c86438d4c27336068ca36c61210af88dc","tid":210110,"uid":13082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T17:38:53.000Z","msg":"超下頻又一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6447ca300be9b5de989eef2e4394772c18f81df1","tid":210110,"uid":64849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:11:27.000Z","msg":"對撚住AMD真係無撚言"},{"pid":"109dac1ff956aa1fa674e64cfb5bd2e248af7ae5","tid":210110,"uid":22424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>超下頻又一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/